Vanessa, pull yourselftogether.
You have to snap out of it!

1218
01:15:13,801 --> 01:15:14,969
You snap out of it.

1219
01:15:15,052 --> 01:15:16,137
You snap out of it.

1220
01:15:16,220 --> 01:15:18,472
-You snap out of it!
-You snap out of it!

