01:20:04,675 --> 01:20:06,427
Little darling

1295
01:20:06,510 --> 01:20:10,514
The smiles returning to the faces

1296
01:20:11,765 --> 01:20:13,142
Little darling

1297
01:20:13,601 --> 01:20:17,438
lt seems like years since it's been here

1298
01:20:19,106 --> 01:20:21,275
Here comes the sun

