Hold it.

1346
01:30:24,711 --> 01:30:28,298
l'm sorry. l'm sorry, everyone.
Can we stop here?

1347
01:30:28,381 --> 01:30:31,802
l'm not making a major life decision
during a production number!

1348
01:30:31,885 --> 01:30:34,971
